# Reversing Cheat Sheet

## ADD Challenge

```asm
add al, K
cmp al, TARGET
```

Reverse:

```python
input = TARGET - K
```

---

## SUB Challenge

```asm
sub al, K
cmp al, TARGET
```

Reverse:

```python
input = TARGET + K
```

---

## XOR Challenge

```asm
xor al, K
cmp al, TARGET
```

Reverse:

```python
input = TARGET ^ K
```

