# Mental Model

```text
AND  -> KEEP bits
OR   -> SET bits
XOR  -> TOGGLE bits

SHL  -> Multiply by powers of 2
SHR  -> Divide by powers of 2

[rdi] -> memory pointed to by rdi
rdi   -> the pointer itself

ret -> return to caller
rax -> return value
```
